data.description: !!! PRICE REDUCED !!! Looking for your dream home that is both convenient and updated? Look no further! This home boasts a prime location that is mere steps away from the best schools, parks, and restaurants in town, making it an ideal living space for any family.. This classic yet modern abode features a charming exterior highlighted by a newer roof and a garage that is rare at this price point, ensuring ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. As you enter the home, you'll immediately be captivated by the stunning white shaker kitchen cabinets, gleaming granite countertops, and contemporary Stainless Steel appliances that effortlessly blend style with functionality. The kitchen also boasts a smooth top electric range, making cooking a breeze. Step outside and you'll discover a gorgeous patio adorned with a charming pergola that is perfect for candlelit dinners, al fresco brunches, and outdoor entertaining. The home is complete with plenty of space for your little ones or furry friends to frolic and play in the yard. Make this home yours today and experience the perfect combination of beauty, comfort, and convenience, at an unbeatable value. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity! Buyer and buyer agent to verify all information provided.
